  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nOnce the Activity Centre is opened, the Navigation panel is inaccessible to the user.\r\nThe Navigation panel is then only available for the user once the Activity centre is not in view.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n- Create a Community\r\n- Create channels within it\r\n- From Settings, enable 'Activity Centre'\r\n- In the channel, open the 'Activity Centre'\r\n- Try selecting any of the options in the navigation panel.\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nThe user must be allowed to select any of the options available\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nThe user is blocked from activating any of the selections\r\n\r\nhttps://www.loom.com/share/7a00fa70006e46e6b4ec2688fef8bf33\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version : base_bc on commit : 1246da663e2471bc22abd4363208f27589cce583\r\n\r\n",
